<b>Grading</b>:
<br>
<br>
Your course grade will be computed as follows: Homework 30%, Midterm 30%, Final 40%.
<br>
<br>

<b>Overview of course</b>
<p>
This course covers Galois theory, commutative algebra, and representations of finite groups.
For more details see the syllabus for the algebra qualifying exam <a href="http://www.math.umass.edu/~hacking/611/qual/index.html">here</a>.
</p>




